headline: Cessna SkyCourier Combi Configuration Achieves Certification From the National Civil Aviation Agency of Brazil
summary: WICHITA, Kan., June 04, 2025--The Cessna SkyCourier Combi configuration recently achieved ANAC certification and joined the fleet of Brazilian charter company Cleiton Táxi Aéreo.
